enb_long_title: United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change: Twenty-Second Session of the Subsidiary Bodies
sentences: COP 11 and COP/MOP I: Secretary of the COP Richard Kinley briefed delegates on preparations for COP 11 and COP/MOP I in Montreal (FCCC/SBI/2005/4 and Corr.1).
AUSTRALIA questioned the need for an agenda item on UNFCCC Article 4.8 and 4.9 at COP 11.
SAUDI ARABIA was satisfied with the current draft agenda.
KENYA, AOSIS, TANZANIA and others raised concerns about visa issues.
